<s> RFC-2396: URI that are hierarchical in nature use the slash "/" character for separating hierarchical components.  </s>
<s> Many URI schemes include a top hierarchical element for a naming authority, such that the namespace defined by the remainder of the  </s>
<s> URI is governed by that authority.  </s>
<s> This authority component is  </s>
