<s> The "info" URI scheme supports hierarchy as indicated by the presence of the slash "/" character.  </s>
<s> Values for the "namespace" component...identify the public namespace in which the (unescaped) value for the "identifier" component originates, and are registered in the "info" Registry, which guarantees their uniqueness.  </s>
